<p align="justify"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;">Reclasificamos el activo. Su valor será el menor de:</span></span></p>
<p align="justify"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;">-</span></span><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;"><i>Valor Contable</i></span></span><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;">= 50.000-20.000(amortización acumulada de los dos años)=30.000</span></span></p>
<p align="justify"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;">-</span></span><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;"><i>Valor Razonable-costes de venta</i></span></span><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;">= 20.000 – 150 = 19.850(Tomamos éste).</span></span></p>
